---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About SMBCyberHub">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">🛡️ About SMBCyberHub</h1>

    <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
      <strong>Cybersecurity. Simplified.</strong><br />
      SMBCyberHub helps small teams become audit-ready, insurer-compliant, and security-aware — in 30 minutes or less.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
      We create downloadable cybersecurity awareness kits for small businesses (1–20 employees). No SaaS platforms, no logins, no bloat — just practical, printable, audit-aligned content you can use right away.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">👤 Who We Are</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      SMBCyberHub is built by a 20+ year IT and cybersecurity veteran with a background in compliance, documentation, and secure systems for small and mid-sized teams.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We’re not a consultancy or a subscription app. We're a <strong>no-fluff product shop</strong> focused on fast, affordable security wins — especially for SMBs without an internal IT team.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">📦 What We Offer</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li><strong>Training decks</strong> that staff actually understand</li>
      <li><strong>Editable policies</strong> aligned to ISO27001 and GDPR</li>
      <li><strong>Awareness posters & checklists</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Staff quizzes</strong> with answer keys</li>
      <li><strong>Onboarding templates</strong> for team leads</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Everything is available as a one-time download — no subscriptions, and you keep the files forever.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">🧠 Why It Works</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>✅ <strong>Offline-ready</strong></li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Audit-aligned</strong></li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Simple to deploy</strong></li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Designed for non-technical users</strong></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We focus on the first 30 minutes: the critical awareness, documentation, and habits that protect your team (and impress your insurer).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">💬 Contact & Support</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Need help or have a suggestion? Reach out via email at
      <a href="mailto:info@smbcyberhub.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@smbcyberhub.com</a> — we respond within 48 hours.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 border-t pt-10">🔐 Trust & Compliance</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
             viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium">GDPR-Aligned Kits</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes policy templates and training content mapped to GDPR Article 39.1(b).</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
             viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium">ISO27001-Friendly</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Policy documents and staff training designed to support Clause 7.2.2 readiness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
             viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium">No Logins Required</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">All kits are ZIP-delivered and offline-ready — no SaaS, tracking, or user accounts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
             viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="font-medium">Solo Founder Model</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Built and maintained by an IT veteran and supported by a small team of specialists - focused entirely on small business needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
